Biography

Broke single season rebounding and steals record in High School

High School:

2 Year Captain... Broke the single season rebounding record and season rebound average record...Tri High School’s All Time Leading Rebounder and Scorer... Hold records for most: Rebounds in a Game, Blocks in a Single Season, Steals in a Single Season, Points Scored by a Freshman... Hold Records Per Game: Career Rebound Average, Season Rebound Average, Points Per Game, Rebounds Per Game... All-County 3 years... All-Area 1st team 3 year... All-Sectional team 3 years... All-Regional Team... All Semi-State Team... All Conference 3 years... also played softball 4 years.

Personal:

The daughter of Misty Jones and Calvin Parham... has 3 siblings Olivia, Finley and Brynn... a exercise science major.
